VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'hands-off. Or you can run one command to install the HyperFrames skills yourself. And you can paste this into the text area of Claude. But either way, once you\'re done, you\'ll be ready to go. All right, so let\'s actually build something. For the first demo, I\'m going'

