VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'is going to look something like this. Create a clean cinematic intro animation for HyperFrames. Dark background, smooth modern motion graphics. And for the title, HyperFrames. For the subtitle, prompt, animate, and render. Subtle glow effects, minimal high-end design, smooth'

